<C>__{psychologist}
<D>__{okay, ronnie, today i will be giving you a psychiatric evaluation to determine if you're competent to enter into the police academy. it's really just a formality. don't want any serial killers working for us, now do we?}
<C>__{ronnie}
<D>__{no, ma'am, we don't.}
<C>__{psychologist}
<D>__{okay, ronnie, so let's start with your background. where are you from?}
<C>__{ronnie}
<D>__{born and raised right here.}
<C>__{psychologist}
<D>__{local boy. okay, and, ronnie, have you ever been convicted of any crimes?}
<C>__{ronnie}
<D>__{no, ma'am. my record is totally clean.}
<C>__{psychologist}
<D>__{do you now take any illegal drugs or have you taken any in the past?}
