<D>__{no, ma'am. i believe drugs are the path to self destruction and should be purged from the face of the earth with ruthless vengeance.}
<C>__{psychologist}
<D>__{any prescription medications?}
<C>__{ronnie}
<D>__{yes, for my nerves. a man in my line of work has a lot of stress to deal with. if you've seen the bloodshed i've seen, you'd be on the meds too. i where are you going with this?}
<C>__{psychologist}
<D>__{are you presently or have you ever been affiliated with the communist party?}
<C>__{ronnie}
<D>__{i can't believe you'd even ask me that.}
