<D>__{okay, here's a real world scenario. you have a gun }
<C>__{ronnie}
<D>__{finally.}
<C>__{psychologist}
<D>__{that wasn't really the question, never mind, i think i got that one. um... here's one. do you feel like you would work well on a team?}
<C>__{ronnie}
<D>__{would i? yes. would i be more useful working alone, i would say definitely. i see myself more like a rambo kind of guy. a man who rolls solo. taking care of business on his own terms. kind of like a superhero or something.}
